name: ComparatorChain_compareTest
description: Unit tests for the compare method in the ComparatorChain class.

test_cases.name: testCompareWithSingleComparatorForwardOrder
test_cases.description: Tests the compare method with a single comparator in forward order.

test_cases.name: testCompareWithSingleComparatorReverseOrder
test_cases.description: Tests the compare method with a single comparator in reverse order.

test_cases.name: testCompareWithMultipleComparators
test_cases.description: Tests the compare method with multiple comparators.

test_cases.name: testCompareWithEmptyChain
test_cases.description: Tests the compare method with an empty comparator chain, expecting an UnsupportedOperationException.

test_cases.name: testCompareAfterModification
test_cases.description: Tests the compare method after modifying the comparator chain, expecting an UnsupportedOperationException.

test_cases.name: testCompareWithMinValuedComparator
test_cases.description: Tests the compare method with a custom comparator that returns Integer.MIN_VALUE or Integer.MAX_VALUE.
